# transports
Infiniband
Omni-Path
RoCE
Cray Gemini and Aries
CUDA
ROCm
Shared Memory
posix, sysv, cma, knem, and xpmem
TCP/IP
NOTE: UCX >= 1.12.0 requires rdma-core >= 28.0 or MLNX_OFED >= 5.0 for Infiniband and RoCE transports support.

